WEBVTT

00:00:58.546 --> 00:01:01.048
hozirgidanam qiyinroq bo'lgan.

00:01:01.048 --> 00:01:02.820
2 500 yil oldin,

00:01:02.820 --> 00:01:05.352
ingliz tili va nemis tili 
bitta til bo'lgan.

00:01:05.352 --> 00:01:06.782
Vaqt sayin ular bir-biridan

00:01:06.782 --> 00:01:10.115
ajrala boshladi, borgan sari 
o'xshashliklari yo'qola bordi.

00:01:10.115 --> 00:01:11.628
Eski ingliz tilida xuddi

00:01:11.628 --> 00:01:12.662
nemis tilidagidek

00:01:12.662 --> 00:01:14.820
jonsiz predmetlarda 'rod' bo'lgan.

00:01:14.820 --> 00:01:17.206
Sanchqi — 'gafol' — ayol 'rod'li edi,

00:01:17.206 --> 00:01:19.190
qoshiq — 'laefel' — erkak 'rod'da,

00:01:19.190 --> 00:01:21.043
stol esa ya'ni 'bord' —

00:01:21.043 --> 00:01:23.786
o'rtacha rodga kiritilgan edi.

00:01:23.786 --> 00:01:24.838
O'zingiz ajrating!

00:01:24.838 --> 00:01:26.329
So'zlarni nafaqat nimani

00:01:26.329 --> 00:01:28.078
anglatishiga qarab, balki uning

00:01:28.078 --> 00:01:30.930
qanday rodda ekanligini bilgan holda 
qo'llash zarur edi.